<li>Eisenschiml, Otto, and Ralph Newman. <i>The Civil War: An American Iliad.</i> New York: Smithmark, 1947. <a href="/entry/Special:BookSources/0831713372" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0831713372</a></li>
