<li>Garrison, Webb. <i>True Tales of the Civil War.</i> New York: Gramercy Books (Random House), 1988. <a href="/entry/Special:BookSources/0517162660" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0517162660</a></li>
<li>Garrison, Webb. <i>Civil War Schemes and Plots.</i> New York: Gramercy Books, 1997. <a href="/entry/Special:BookSources/0517162873" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0517162873</a></li>
