<li>Ragan, Mark K. <i>Submarine Warfare in the Civil War.</i> Cambridge, MA: Da Capo Press, 1999. <a href="/entry/Special:BookSources/0306811979" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0306811979</a></li>
